{"tid":2369571,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村拓哉大女兒不保守了！「破尺度露北半球」驚豔12萬人","createTime":"2021-01-17T09:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T17:35:05.000Z","uid":16659,"like":16,"dislike":446,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"5f4f8020dd5370e395be412553f79bc7805f7df4","tid":2369571,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:09:13.000Z","msg":"「日劇天王」木村拓哉與工藤靜香17歲女兒木村光希跟19歲的姊姊心美也追隨爸媽腳步出道，可說是日本背景最強大的星二代之一，姊妹倆時常開直播和網友互動，IG的追蹤人數已破百萬。一向走清新氣質路線的木村心美，在近日分享了性感露肩照，引起話題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/09/2545361-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F09%2F2545361-XXL.jpg&h=28116ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼木村光希跟木村心美。（圖／翻攝自木村光希IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/30/2635426-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F30%2F2635426-PH.jpg&h=2a267770&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n木村拓哉的小女兒木村光希以「最強星二代」身份出道後沒多久，姊姊木村心美也以藝名Cocomi入行，造成極大話題。木村拓哉一家4口可說是有任何風吹草動都能攻占日本新聞版面。近日姊妹倆都受邀成為迪奧化粧品代言，喜歡紅色的木村心美，特地穿上一件紅色露肩禮服，難得展現性感一面，才一天就獲得12萬讚，相當驚人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/17/2987748-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F17%2F2987748-PH.jpg&h=db75c3b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼木村心美穿上紅色低胸禮服。（圖／翻攝自木村心美IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/17/2987749-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F17%2F2987749-PH.jpg&h=1afb1c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n木村光希每次要跟姊姊心美開直播，都會事先請粉絲提供想知道的問題，並在直播中回答，之前姊妹倆被問到心中理想型男友，認真提出手好看、聲音低沉、有背肌、肩膀寬、適合穿西裝，以及「能好好保護我」等6大條件，說完之後，木村光希忍不住心中嚮往，脫口說出：「好想早點結婚喔！」<br />\n<br />\n有趣的是，姊妹倆開出的條件，爸爸木村拓哉全都完美符合，這也讓網友笑說「果然爸爸是理想型」、「喜歡的男生條件跟爸爸好像」、「說的就是木村啊」。其實，木村光希跟木村心美聊起家庭生活時，總是處處流露出對爸爸的崇拜，也曾直接說希望找「一個像爸爸一樣的人」當男友，讓網友苦笑直呼：「難度太高啦！」"},{"pid":"eb54650abd0e3feb4b3f2dcc80411a106d46a190","tid":2369571,"uid":155818,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:10:08.000Z","msg":"低胸?"},{"pid":"1e4c26dff5cf82e2de5b28da38198c8c1fcf0afa","tid":2369571,"uid":108078,"like":810,"dislike":1,"score":809,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:14:02.000Z","msg":"北半球?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407c65dcbaf4454bd233938372db990561d2a7b9","tid":2369571,"uid":128705,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:19:11.000Z","msg":"球呢？"},{"pid":"8b2ec4fff48b9da6d2c6a1aedd83877408690efc","tid":2369571,"uid":128705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d21e22ac01b23daf4b27fd245b83396a80f6b6","tid":2369571,"uid":266968,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:20:33.000Z","msg":"球呢?"},{"pid":"016d6fa83e718d1c5f085631562b80983b4a2bec","tid":2369571,"uid":37447,"like":162,"dislike":1,"score":161,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"上面淡妝靚過濃妝好多喎"},{"pid":"72700a0008813227c330dba1c1d93f4be909dc91","tid":2369571,"uid":120575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:21:23.000Z","msg":"半球？"},{"pid":"7427749996380942d2a2c3c656fb13584706e8d5","tid":2369571,"uid":170760,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"北機場"},{"pid":"8d7ae45f044d8e054f9da60fbc4984a269c6a9aa","tid":2369571,"uid":237459,"like":220,"dislike":2,"score":218,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"得個北極<br />\n邊有北半球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170173dac6d2fefa082f0d4469dadc7a7b2b65f4","tid":2369571,"uid":200280,"like":23,"dislike":54,"score":-31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T09:23:20.000Z","msg":"大女好撚醜"},{"pid":"7c3741f97ce00403e2d11d97e42366b9002afb82","t